# game options

## Feature

this checks all the collusion in game.

### Scenario:when ball hits the horizontal boundary

given: players are playing the game
when ball hits the horizontal boundary
then change the direction of the ball

### Scenario: when ball hits the wall behind the player

given:players are playing the game
when ball hits the wall behind the player
then increase the score of other player

### Scenario: when ball hits the racket

given:players are playing the game
when ball hits the racket
then change the direction of the ball
